
 The C sources of Idio are documented suitable for kernel-doc.

 kernel-doc is in the LinuxDoc suite.

https://return42.github.io/linuxdoc/linuxdoc-howto/index.html

Install
=======

pip
---

 wget https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
 rpm -i epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
 yum install python2-pip
 pip install --upgrade pip

LinuxDoc
--------

 pip install git+http://github.com/return42/linuxdoc.git

